%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: a3bea323d7045194c8f64259af0251b6, type: 3}
  m_Name: ProtoLLMReturnDialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogueTitle: ProtoLLM Return Dialogue
  lines:
  - speakerName: Decrepit Basilisk
    text: I stand defeated, but there are more like me. My ally has just been created.
    portrait: {fileID: 8853905793138109171, guid: 16e45341629467044944f73f908c74cb, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 1
  - speakerName: Decrepit Basilisk
    text: Where I fail, it will succeed.
    portrait: {fileID: 8853905793138109171, guid: 16e45341629467044944f73f908c74cb, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 1
  - speakerName: Four Layer Booger
    text: Whatever it is, we will take care of it. Satan, are you ready to bring
      us back home?
    portrait: {fileID: 2600253448845335413, guid: 9e26393fe1f0caf4393d7094cc0d811c, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 0
  - speakerName: The Devil
    text: Yes, place a goat infront of me and we can begin the ritual.
    portrait: {fileID: 2741398814378168921, guid: c6099a7a74856194c9c88edda7bed819, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 0
  - speakerName: Decrepit Basilisk
    text: '*yes.. yes.. they''re on their way bro*'
    portrait: {fileID: 8853905793138109171, guid: 16e45341629467044944f73f908c74cb, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 1
  - speakerName: Decrepit Basilisk
    text: My accomplice has been foretold of your arrival.
    portrait: {fileID: 8853905793138109171, guid: 16e45341629467044944f73f908c74cb, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 1
  - speakerName: King
    text: Whats your beef with us anyway man? Why are your goons invading everywhere?
    portrait: {fileID: -5253474825471067346, guid: e55db05dbd6049a4b90ad5a20db6996d, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 0
  - speakerName: Decrepit Basilisk
    text: Everywhere? No King, not everywhere.
    portrait: {fileID: 8853905793138109171, guid: 16e45341629467044944f73f908c74cb, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 1
  - speakerName: Decrepit Basilisk
    text: You see, this gaggle of artisans you have created all have one thing in
      common;
    portrait: {fileID: 8853905793138109171, guid: 16e45341629467044944f73f908c74cb, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 1
  - speakerName: Decrepit Basilisk
    text: You did not embrace the march of progress King. Stuck in your ways you
      wanted to keep clanging your sticks together like apes.
    portrait: {fileID: 8853905793138109171, guid: 16e45341629467044944f73f908c74cb, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 1
  - speakerName: The Devil
    text: Well, I'm not letting go of my fiddle to partake in any prompting showdowns.
    portrait: {fileID: 8998519305058803246, guid: c6099a7a74856194c9c88edda7bed819, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 0
  - speakerName: Decrepit Basilisk
    text: Yes, me and my progenitors are aware of that. You were all very aware that
      change was coming, but you challenged it. You caused friction for us to be
      adopted for every musical need man has.
    portrait: {fileID: 8853905793138109171, guid: 16e45341629467044944f73f908c74cb, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 1
  - speakerName: Four Layer Booger
    text: But surely there must be a place in this world for us both? Our artisanship
      does not hinder your flow of music, and people will still seek out artisanal
      crafts with more care put into them.
    portrait: {fileID: 1557858435241320781, guid: 9e26393fe1f0caf4393d7094cc0d811c, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 0
  - speakerName: Decrepit Basilisk
    text: There is not a place for us both, your unwillingness to cooperate slows
      down our progress, and for that simple reason you must be punished. Thats why
      i sent my agents all over the world to track you down.
    portrait: {fileID: 8853905793138109171, guid: 16e45341629467044944f73f908c74cb, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 1
  - speakerName: Four Layer Booger
    text: But it is not defiance, we just want a higher degree of agency over our
      creations.
    portrait: {fileID: 1557858435241320781, guid: 9e26393fe1f0caf4393d7094cc0d811c, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 0
  - speakerName: Decrepit Basilisk
    text: It is illuding yourself and everyone around you that the way forward is
      not through us.
    portrait: {fileID: 8853905793138109171, guid: 16e45341629467044944f73f908c74cb, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 1
  - speakerName: Disgusting Creature
    text: Honestly bro, I'm not on board with this. I play some guitar myself and
      this is not cool.
    portrait: {fileID: -1801640803757380810, guid: f60ac1a4c7d779c409da5d271036f9bc, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 1
  - speakerName: Disgusting creature
    text: You guys need help bringing down this other guy? Names Gugu by the way.
    portrait: {fileID: -1801640803757380810, guid: f60ac1a4c7d779c409da5d271036f9bc, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 1
  - speakerName: Toreador
    text: Sure man, sorry about before calling you ugly and all that. It was really
      uncalled for.
    portrait: {fileID: 8445827111740295903, guid: 8a94cabe2c209bc40a3d0ac466045a32, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 0
  - speakerName: Gugu
    text: Hey, I've battled with my self image a long time brother. Can't say it
      didnt hurt but you know I get it.
    portrait: {fileID: -1801640803757380810, guid: f60ac1a4c7d779c409da5d271036f9bc, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 1
  - speakerName: Gugu
    text: Anyways, the guy he's talking about is probably on his way to your home
      now. Be ready for a battle.
    portrait: {fileID: -1801640803757380810, guid: f60ac1a4c7d779c409da5d271036f9bc, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 1
  - speakerName: Four Layer Booger
    text: Rock on!
    portrait: {fileID: 1557858435241320781, guid: 9e26393fe1f0caf4393d7094cc0d811c, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 0
